{"tid":2352610,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"墨爾本華商被指涉及外國滲透 面臨驅逐出境","createTime":"2021-01-04T06:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T11:08:28.000Z","uid":41404,"like":187,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd30e7954dfd8229f7e22a54be65ab34766f65e","tid":2352610,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/melbourne-based-chinese-businessman-huifeng-haha-liu-assessed-as-national-security-risk-facing-deportation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fmelbourne-based-chinese-businessman-huifeng-haha-liu-assessed-as-national-security-risk-facing-deportation&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyfrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=86855f20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/melbourne-based-chinese-businessman-huifeng-haha-liu-assessed-as-national-security-risk-facing-deportation</a>"},{"pid":"b3100bea11617ee8bf921c178e2faede712303a1","tid":2352610,"uid":41404,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:37:16.000Z","msg":"澳洲廣播公司報道，該名華商劉輝峰Huifeng &ldquo;Haha&rdquo; Liu，是自由黨捐助者，做過中國人民解放軍，與聯邦自由黨議員廖嬋娥及助理財長蘇卡（Michael Sukkar）建立了聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n52歲的劉輝峰正就面臨驅逐出境，提出反駁。聯邦政府基於涉及國家安全風險，拒批劉輝峰的永居申請。聯邦警方也證實反外國滲透工作小組正調查。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述劉輝峰說，相信澳洲安全情報局評估他對國家安全構成風險，因為他是一個澳洲華人鄰里互助組織的主席，該組織有協議，同意接受中國駐墨爾本領館的指示。"},{"pid":"3e61383adf9fcc0a0d8b1c8af370781b38260bde","tid":2352610,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"907985a35485912bbb6ea0a772f11a3644801851","tid":2352610,"uid":59283,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:37:56.000Z","msg":"haha <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350f42e5afe98d44397a1968efd05d49f40618fc","tid":2352610,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":