bece22f8783d","tid":2352610,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3100bea11617ee8bf921c178e2faede712303a1","tid":2352610,"uid":41404,"like":135,"dislike":0,"score":135,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:37:16.000Z","msg":"澳洲廣播公司報道，該名華商劉輝峰Huifeng &ldquo;Haha&rdquo; Liu，是自由黨捐助者，做過中國人民解放軍，與聯邦自由黨議員廖嬋娥及助理財長蘇卡（Michael Sukkar）建立了聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n52歲的劉輝峰正就面臨驅逐出境，提出反駁。聯邦政府基於涉及國家安全風險，拒批劉輝峰的永居申請。聯邦警方也證實反外國滲透工作小組正調查。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述劉輝峰說，相信澳洲安全情報局評估他對國家安全構成風險，因為他是一個澳洲華人鄰里互助組織的主席，該組織有協議，同意接受中國駐墨爾本領館的指示。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"fe2a392a2d865d08840d5d8609bbf3177aab534b","tid":2352610,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:50:24.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"ec71405a9fc80982267f9c528ba20307acb74b8e","tid":2352610,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ce5622fc3133db73cdbf11178d8a436115ab4a15","tid":2352610,"uid":13343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51178be934e6c485dc6aa8f7c1f2dc6a7765397d","tid":2352610,"uid":306614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ae30e23097ab73582a079e1685449995617c12c7","tid":2352610,"uid":167928,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"與<span class=\"red\">聯邦自由黨議員廖嬋娥</span>及<span class=\"red\">助理財長蘇卡</span>（Michael Sukkar）建立了聯繫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"wow CCP indirectly infiltrates Austrlian politics ar"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:41:00.000Z","msg":"廖嬋娥講咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"所以啲人一味話工黨奶共就好笑，根本2邊都有鬼，唔知頭唔知路一味非黑即白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29167827f25880315321a5